  "faqAnswer4": "Open Friends from the menu, search by name or email, and send a friend request. Once accepted, you can invite them to rooms.",
  "faqQuestion5": "How do I cancel my Premium subscription?",
  "faqAnswer5": "Manage or cancel your subscription anytime from the Google Play Store's Subscriptions section.",
  "faqQuestion6": "Is my watch history private?",
  "faqAnswer6": "Yes — your watch history is tied to your account and only visible to you.",
